	)
	(text "HOST VBUS INRUSH LIMITER\n\nU11 OUTPUT RAMP ≈ 26.6 ms WITH C72 = 10 nF.\nR48/C71 DELAY ENABLE.\nD6 RAPIDLY RESETS THE DELAY AFTER UNPLUG.\nQOD IS INTENTIONALLY LEFT OPEN.\n\nU11 LIMITS THE DIRECT HOST-VBUS PATH.\nTHE EXTERNAL 5 V INPUT BYPASSES U11."
